{"word":"ἠῷος","slug":"ἠῷος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἠῷος</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>= <a href='S:ἠοῖος'><el>ἠοῖος</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>at morn, at break of day</i>, <b>Hhymn.</b>, <b><a href='S:Hesiod'>Hes.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>from the east, eastern</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>from <a href='S:ἠώς'><el>ἠώς</el></a>\n"}]}